/datum/category_item/catalogue/technology/drone/hivebot/rapid // Hivebot Scanner Data - This is for rapid Hivebots
	name = "Hivebot - Gunner"
	desc = "A model of hivebot with a vastly improved version of the magentic weapon that more common ranged models use. \
	The complex components that fit in the hivebot's less crude magentic weapon probably preclude this version of the \
	hivebot as being as common as ranged cousins. Still its a comparitively primitive ranged fighter that makes up for \
	its limitations with sheer numbers."
	value = CATALOGUER_REWARD_EASY

/datum/category_item/catalogue/technology/drone/hivebot/laser // Hivebot Scanner Data - This is for Laser Hivebots
	name = "Hivebot - Laser"
	desc = "Yellowish or golden armor marks more advanced models of hivebots. This particular model is equipped with an unusual \
	blue beamed laser weapon. Though it has some color similarities to fearsome pulse weapons this laser is comparitively underpowered \
	even compared to red lasers. Despite its limitations the laser is still deadly to targets without protection and can overwhelm even \
	well armored targets with volume, something hivebots excell at."
	value = CATALOGUER_REWARD_EASY

/datum/category_item/catalogue/technology/drone/hivebot/ion // Hivebot Scanner Data - This is for Ion Hivebots
	name = "Hivebot - Ion"
	desc = "Yellowish or golden armor marks more advanced models of hivebots. This model is equipped with ion weapons. Ion hivebots have been \
	record since the earliest encounters with hivebots making many question why such a model exists. Theories range from the hivebots having \
	previously fought rogue synthetics even rogue hivebots to the hivebots having created the model quickly after its first encounters with \
	mechs and energy weapons. Regardless of its origin, it fills a crucial niche in the ranks of the hivebots, providing a way to shutdown \
	enemy synthetics and energy weapons at very low cost per unit."
	value = CATALOGUER_REWARD_EASY

