	name = "Reinforced Hivebot"
	desc = "An further improved version of the hivebot gunner, with its standard plating swapped for a stronger alloy. Though its unknown \
	why most hivebots do not use this same tough allow many speculate the upgraded alloy take longer to forge compared to that of the  \
	standard plating, causing this armor only to be reserved only for more advanced units."
	value = CATALOGUER_REWARD_EASY

/datum/category_item/catalogue/technology/drone/hivebot/fire // Hivebot Scanner Data - This is for flamer Hivebots
	name = "Incendiary Hivebot"
	desc = "A hivebot equipped witha  primtive firespitting weapon. Though relatively underpowered the hivebot incindiary \
	weapon is a marvel of engineering an incendiary weapon powered almost entirely be electricity. The weapons suggests \
	that the creators of the hivebots had highly advanced knowledge of electrical engineering and sythetic chemistry which \
	only leads to further questions of why many of the hivebot's other features are lacking."
	value = CATALOGUER_REWARD_EASY

/datum/category_item/catalogue/technology/drone/hivebot/lobber
	name = "Lobber Hivebot"
	desc = "The 'lobber' is a sized down version of the more dangerous bombard hivebot. The novel energy weapon equipped \
	as its primary weapon has made the robot a terror to SDF and militia trying to hold the line against the hivebot hordes, \
	who are often scattered by the arcing attacks of the lobber and its larger cousin."
	value = CATALOGUER_REWARD_EASY

/datum/category_item/catalogue/technology/drone/hivebot/siege
	name = "Siege Hivebot"
	desc = "By far the most dangerous units of hivebot produced the siege series of hivebots take the modularity of the hivebot \
	and apply it to long range weapons. Whether fragmentation grenade firing 'mortars', emp slinging 'ionics', or radiation cleansing \
	'devastators' these siege bots are singelahandedly responsible for the greatest victories of the hivebots often again unprepared \
	militias and SDF who are pushed from defensive positions and scattered by their long range bombardments."
	value = CATALOGUER_REWARD_HARD

/datum/category_item/catalogue/technology/drone/hivebot/coil
	name = "Piercer Hivebot"
	desc = "The piercer is hivebot equipped with a powerful magentic flechette gun. Compared to the weapons of other hivebots the \
	Piercer is a true weapons of modern war. While lesser hivebots use low velocity weapons more useful for killing pests. The \
	armor piercing flechettes of the piercer can penetrate even the most protective armors. It is suggested that the Piercer was \
	first developed as the hivebot's answer to Unathi breacher RiGs and it has been a fitting answer indeed."
	value = CATALOGUER_REWARD_HARD
